high_descs: MOve to the sink to the right of the stove
Pick up a spoon from the sink
Move to the stove behind you
Put the spoon on a pan on the stove
Pick up a pan from the stove with the spoon
Move to the sink to the right
Put the pan in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a pan in the sink with a spoon in it.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the stove top, then turn right to the sink.
Pick up the spoon out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the stove top.
Put the spoon in the pan on the stove top.
Pick up the pan from the stove top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the pan with the spoon in it inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a spoon in it inside a sink basin.

high_descs: Turn to your right then walk straight then head to the sink
Pick up the spoon in the sink
Turn to your left and head to the stove
Place the spoon in the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan with spoon on the stove
Turn to your right and walk towards the sink
Put the pan with spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with spoon in the sink
